      "content": "# How to Scrim\n\n**Keep the Same**\nHere is the list of all settings you NEED to keep the same when joining a scrims game:\n- The gamemode & teamsize\n- The region\n- The join code\n\n**Using Yunite for Code**\nMost severs do not send the code itself, but rather use the Yunite Bot which adds to code for you. Remember that this is for a specific scrims server and the channel names, etc will likely be different in other servers but the whole process is still the same. \n\n__Here's how you can use the Yunite Bot for scrims: <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j8DbOGqvCjs>__\n\n**How to Enable Tournament Settings**\n<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HaaMTcsQfwo>\n\n**Scrim Servers:**\n> - #\uD83C\uDFC3‍♂️・scrims-servers",
